# LibraryAPI â€“ Books API (requires X-API-Key; default in Development: DefaultApiKey123)
@LibraryAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5250
@ApiKey = DefaultApiKey123

### GET all books
GET {{LibraryAPI_HostAddress}}/Books
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

###

### GET book by id
GET {{LibraryAPI_HostAddress}}/Books/1
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Accept: application/json

###

### POST new book
POST {{LibraryAPI_HostAddress}}/Books
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Book",
  "author": "Author Name",
  "isbn": "978-0-00-000000-0",
  "publishedDate": "2026-01-01",
  "owner": "Owner Name",
  "borrower": ""
}

###

### PUT update book
PUT {{LibraryAPI_HostAddress}}/Books/1
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "author": "Author Name",
  "isbn": "978-0-00-000000-0",
  "publishedDate": "2026-01-01",
  "owner": "Owner Name",
  "borrower": "Johny"
}

###

### DELETE book
DELETE {{LibraryAPI_HostAddress}}/Books/1
X-API-Key: {{ApiKey}}
